<concept id="concept_3413BBD173324104B42FB714974CABE7" xml:lang="en-us">
            <title>Managing Payment Types</title>
            <conbody>

                                    <section>
                                                <p>You are responsible for specifying how your customers and the customers of your brokers may pay for their subscriptions:</p>
                                                <ul>
                                                            <li>On receipt of invoice.</li>
                                                            <li>With credit card.</li>
                                                            <li>By direct debit.</li>
                                                </ul>
                                    </section>
                        
                        <section id="For_details_refer_to_concept_conbody_section_2">
                                    <p><ph
                                                            conref="../../help/tasks/organization_managePaymentEnablement.xml#task634/Your_operator_is_responsible_task_taskbody_context_p_2_ph"
                                                /></p>
                                    <!--p><ph
                                                            conref="../../help/tasks/organization_managePaymentEnablement.xml#task634/If_you_request_a_payment_type_task_taskbody_context_p_3_ph"
                                                /></p>
                                    <p><ph audience="doc"> For details, refer to <xref
                                                            href="../Billing/c_BillUsePSP.xml"/>.</ph></p-->
                                    <p><ph conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                                                            /> allows you to specify the payment types for individual customers and individual services used by the customers. <ph
                                                            conref="../../help/tasks/organization_managePaymentEnablement.xml#task634/If_you_decide_to_offer_more_t_task_taskbody_context_p_4_ph"
                                                /></p>
                                    <p
                                                conref="../../help/tasks/organization_managePaymentEnablement.xml#task634/Be_aware_of_the_following_eff_task_taskbody_context_p_5"/>
                                    <ul>
                                                <li
                                                            conref="../../help/tasks/organization_managePaymentEnablement.xml#task634/If_you_remove_a_used_payment_task_taskbody_context_ul_li"/>
                                                <li
                                                            conref="../../help/tasks/organization_managePaymentEnablement.xml#task634/If_you_remove_a_used_payment2_task_taskbody_context_ul_li"/>
                                    </ul>
                                    <p>To specify the payment types, use the <uicontrol>Manage payment types</uicontrol> menu option in the <uicontrol>Customer</uicontrol> menu of the <ph
                                                            conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                                                /> administration portal.</p>
                                    <note id="In_specific_scenarios_your_o_concept_conbody_section_1_n"
                                                >In specific scenarios, your operator may deactivate any possibilities for customers to select payment types and specify billing addresses. If this is the case, the definition of payment types is not possible.</note>
                        </section>
            </conbody>
</concept>
